criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  stable chronic kidney disease

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  unable/unwilling to give informed consent;

          -  pregnant or breast-feeding;

          -  known allergy to shellfish, iodine or inulin;

          -  have evidence of impaired bladder emptying defined as a post-void residual of greater
             than 20 ml.
